com.citytechinc.cq.component.annotations.widgets

Annotation Type Switch


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
 @Target(value={FIELD,METHOD})
public @interface Switch
    Represents a Widget of type granite/ui/components/foundation/form/switch in Touch UI

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String checked
      Indicates if the checkbox is checked.
      boolean ignoreData
      If false, the checked status is based on matching the form values by name and value properties.
      String offText
      The text for “On”.
      String onText
      The text for “Off”.

    • Element Detail

      • offText

        public abstract String offText
        The text for “On”.
        Returns:
        String
        Default:
        ""

      • onText

        public abstract String onText
        The text for “Off”.
        Returns:
        String
        Default:
        ""

      • checked

        public abstract String checked
        Indicates if the checkbox is checked. Providing checked property (either true or false) will imply ignoreData to be true.

        The only valid values are "true" and "false"

        Returns:
        String
        Default:
        ""

      • ignoreData

        public abstract boolean ignoreData
        If false, the checked status is based on matching the form values by name and value properties. Otherwise, the form values are not matched, and the checked status is based on checked property specified.
        Returns:
        boolean
        Default:
        false
